name: aircraft production, agricultural | aircraft, agricultural | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/28303/documentation

This dataset models the manufacturing of an agricultural airplane. It should be used ONLY for similar agricultural applications.

The activity starts by receiving/obtaining the material inputs required for construction at the factory gate. 

This activity ends with the production of the agricultural aircraft. The activity ends with the production of one aircraft. The dataset includes the materials (aluminium, titanium, nickel and composite materials), energy (electricity and heat), and water used in the production. Emissions of VOCs are also included. Emissions from the production of composite materials are included via an input of carbon fibre reinforced plastic. Electronics and interior materials (plastics, textiles etc.) have not been included due to a lack of available data.
category: C:Manufacturing/30:Manufacture of other transport equipment/303:Manufacture of air and spacecraft and related machinery/3030:Manufacture of air and spacecraft and related machinery
tags: Sector: Agriculture & Animal Husbandry; Infrastructure & Machinery

processDocumentation.geographyDescription: The aircraft is modelled to be representative for a global geography .
processDocumentation.technologyDescription: It has a lifetime of 20 years and an operation capacity of 160ha/hour. It weights 2012 kg.
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: This dataset was modelled based on "aircraft production, passenger aircraft, very short haul, GLO" and inputs/outputs were scaled down based on the avarage weight of the agricultural aircraft. (avarage 2012 kg).References "Jemioło W., Cox B., Solvoli G., 2015. Life cycle assessment of current and future passenger air transport in Switzerland, Technology Assessment Group, Laboratory for Energy System Analysis Paul Scherrer Institut (PSI), Switzerland, Mater Thesis  Available at. https://www.sccer-mobility.ch/export/sites/sccer-mobility/capacity-areas/dwn_capacity_areas/Jemiolo_Thesis_Final.pdf"                          (Air Tractor, 2022. Agriculture Aircraft, Air Tractor, INC Available at: https://airtractor.com/aircraft/at-402b/; Aviastar, 2022. Embraer EMB-200/201 Ipanema,  Aviastar  Available at: http://www.aviastar.org/air/brazil/embraer_ipanema.php)
